lead_paragraph: A waterspout uprooted an inflatable house with three children inside it on a Fort Lauderdale beach, sending the toy home flying above palm trees, across a parking lot and over four lanes of traffic.

headline.print_headline: Florida: Children Hurt as Bounce House Takes Flight
headline.main: Florida: Children Hurt as Bounce House Takes Flight

snippet: A waterspout uprooted an inflatable house with three children inside it on a Fort Lauderdale beach, sending the toy home flying above palm trees, across a parking lot and over four lanes of traffic.
abstract: Three children are injured when waterspout uproots inflatable bounce house in Fort Lauderdale, Fla.
